name: Lost#2  2°56’41”S 60°40’33”W
description:
The place

It's been a couple of moons and I'm still stuck here inhabiting this creature. Now I have no communication with others. The possibility of rescue decreases.
I found this place. I'm not sure what it is about or where it is taking me. She does not like it. She gets angry when I approach her, she even becomes more hostile than usual. Her anger boils under my feet. I must earn her trust. I do not know how.
I'm so tired, just like my supplies, my existence runs out.
